{"tid":384771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"食完米線覺得自己好撚低賤","createTime":"2017-09-02T15:10:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-02T16:44:22.000Z","uid":81684,"like":13,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"defb89852be48b8ab65688623a555c96aa3dff67","tid":384771,"uid":81684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:10:04.000Z","msg":"間間米線都請埋啲大陸婆<br />\n講嘢又唔撚正<br />\n我又聽唔明呢啲唔咸唔淡嘅廣東話<br />\n就好似我識英文但聽唔明賓妹講英文咁<br />\n我聽唔明都算<br />\n落單嘅大陸婆竟然聽唔到我嗌米線<br />\n然後比撚咗兜紅薯粉我<br />\n聽佢答人地嘢飲幾錢我都聽唔明<br />\n唔係條仔我都唔會去食米線<br />\n咩譚仔我幾年前陪同事食過一次之後就無再去<br />\n譚仔真係我底線<br />\n又唔好食又唔抵食<br />\n鐘意食呢啲仲要酸辣嘅都係留住大陸種嘅血<br />\n我寧願食車仔麵幫襯啲陀地女人好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5244f75df0dcb344d92f9f0736e283ca877a7f6","tid":384771,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":18,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:38:21.000Z","msg":"唔好飲東江水<br />\n大陸雞<br />\n菜都唔好食"},{"pid":"9abf5f710630fa1629f87e4ac52e9086fe32ed30","tid":384771,"uid":28624,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:43:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好飲東江水<br />\n大陸雞<br />\n菜都唔好食</blockquote><br />\n邊個想食支那用支那d垃圾野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99183ac630a1b314a4b0441e4c8e012fc3dbb872","tid":384771,"uid":30633,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T16:21:52.000Z","msg":"多嘗中國菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://sciencenotes.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/PeriodicTableWorks.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsciencenotes.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F07%2FPeriodicTableWorks.png&h=8512d311&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"31feb627cadf18124175615f7a279b64f9c70738","tid":384771,"uid":81684,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T16:43:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好飲東江水<br />\n大陸雞<br />\n菜都唔好食</blockquote><br />\n你奶大陸老母閪啦去<br />\n廢老logic<br />\n啲臭屍水家陣香港無撚比錢咩<br />\n屋企比貴啲買外國嘢都唔撚買中國食材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3951c4331392595743c6fc942c5a7a5909b8ec6","tid":384771,"uid":81684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T16:44:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多嘗中國菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://sciencenotes.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/PeriodicTableWorks.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsciencenotes.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F07%2FPeriodicTableWorks.png&h=8512d311&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n我喺香港啲餐廳食中菜<br />\n唔撚係大陸婆serve我喎<br />\n就算係大陸種 廣東話都好pro囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}